description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 3 of 4 of the live July match up between The Dragons and Team Ice. The only real non-scripted sex wresting in the world!
Team Ice is down hundreds of points going into the last round of Wrestling. It is gut check time. Ariel X start on the mat against the rookie Holly Heart. Does team Ice have anything left to make a run for the win? Can they trap the Dragon in a double team and make her cum repeatably?
The answer is no, however they do comeback with in a hundred points and make a serious run, but the clock runs out and The Dragons are still undefeated!.
